query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND (cn.name like '%MGM Studios%' OR cn.name like '%Blumhouse Productions%' OR cn.name like '%Universal Pictures%' OR cn.name like '%20th Century Fox%' OR cn.name like '%DreamWorks Animation%') AND cn.country_code in ('sz','am','il','az','bm') AND (chn.name like '%Gamora%') AND (mc.note like '%Italy%' OR mc.note like '%UK%' OR mc.note like '%Russia%' OR mc.note like '%Japan%' OR mc.note like '%Brazil%') AND it3.info in ('LD dynamic range','death date','LD aspect ratio','LD analog left','spouse','sound mix','LD color information','printed media reviews','LD picture format','LD quality program') AND n.name not like '%J%' AND n.gender not in ('m') AND cct2.kind in ('complete','complete+verified','cast') AND it.info in ('runtimes','LD video artifacts','other works','LD label','LD video quality','taglines','LD sharpness','novel','gross') AND (an.name like '%m%' OR an.name like '%O%' OR an.name like '%e%') AND cct1.kind in ('cast','complete','crew') AND (t.title like '%starship%' OR t.title like '%guitar%') AND t.production_year > 1993 AND t.production_year < 1999 AND (pi.note like '%MF%' OR pi.note like '%Edward Bosco%')
